Gospodine Darsi!

00:32:56.027 --> 00:32:58.028
Bridžit?

00:33:00.776 --> 00:33:02.776
Tako si mi nedostajala.

00:33:09.010 --> 00:33:11.010
Kasnimo li?

00:33:12.028 --> 00:33:14.276
Sutra letim za Kartum.

00:33:51.693 --> 00:33:54.401
<i>Žao mi je, Mark.
